295
00:41:06,900 --> 00:41:09,209
In the name of science.

296
00:41:09,660 --> 00:41:13,778
And now I want him back!
- You do not own this man. Stop it!

297
00:41:14,580 --> 00:41:16,969
I want him back!
- So you can beat him?

298
00:41:17,420 --> 00:41:20,651
