334
00:43:58,420 --> 00:44:02,857
He has trouble with certain sounds
because of the constrictive deformity.

335
00:44:03,300 --> 00:44:07,134
But he can talk.
- Is he able to understand?

336
00:44:08,780 --> 00:44:10,771
Yes. Oh, yes.

337
00:44:11,220 --> 00:44:17,216
Except he's so anxious to make a good
impression, that he might be nervous.

338
00:44:34,300 --> 00:44:35,415
Come in!

339
00:44:51,460 --> 00:44:54,770
