00:48:46,740 --> 00:48:49,095
Come and see me in my office
when you're through.

385
00:48:49,540 --> 00:48:52,008
There's something
important I want to say.

386
00:48:52,940 --> 00:48:56,535
Goodbye.
I do hope we shall meet again.

387
00:49:06,140 --> 00:49:09,769
Why didn't you tell me you can read?

388
00:49:10,220 --> 00:49:12,336
I was frightened.

389
00:49:12,780 --> 00:49:19,492
I see.
- I was afraid to talk.

390
00:49:22,980 --> 00:49:25,289
Please forgive me.

391
00:49:35,460 --> 00:49:39,851
