409
00:51:47,900 --> 00:51:50,368
And how do you get tickets to see him?

410
00:51:50,820 --> 00:51:53,414
Your very own Sunny Jim!
- Let's go and see him!

411
00:51:53,860 --> 00:51:57,011
Keep your shirt on.
The time must be right.

412
00:51:59,100 --> 00:52:04,299
Now he's in the attic, but tomorrow
they'll move him to Bedstead Square,

413
00:52:04,740 --> 00:52:09,018
