Friends...

461
00:57:34,140 --> 00:57:36,813
Here is Frederick's mother.

462
00:57:41,820 --> 00:57:44,732
And these are my parents.

463
00:57:50,340 --> 00:57:55,016
They have such noble faces.

464
00:57:56,900 --> 00:57:59,778
Yes, I've always thought so myself.

