499
01:01:23,020 --> 01:01:23,975
No.

500
01:01:25,700 --> 01:01:27,019
I thought not.

501
01:01:37,820 --> 01:01:39,378
Come in.

502
01:01:40,780 --> 01:01:41,656
Good morning!

